      "reviews": [
        {
          "reviewTitle": "No makeup makeup",
          "reviewText": "Sheglam is underrated. All products I have tried by this brand exceed my expectations and I just want to keep trying more. This foundation is at the top of my list. I have FINALLY gotten the foundation and shade of my dreams. The perfect no makeup makeup at a reasonable price. I bought a fluffy foundation brush separately to apply the product which gave me the look I was hoping to achieve with a small amount of product used. The product is thick, but with the brush and a small amount used, the product goes on easily. The foundation gives a matte finish with full coverage, perfect for on the go days when you don\u2019t feel like doing a full face look. I will definitely repurchase and keep buying more Sheglam!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on March 4, 2026",
