          "reviewTitle": "Good color and consistency",
          "reviewText": "So far so good ! I like this! Full coverage but able to blend it down to sheer. The color is good for me. I usually pick foundation in shade porcelain. I have had good luck with Revlon colorstay 130 and Maybelline fit me mattte 110. This sheglam fair is a good match for my very fair skin! I will try more products from Sheglam!",
